<lb n="0401a24" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0401a2401">此&CB00057;隨誦即成。一日三時一一時中誦一百
<lb n="0401a25" ed="T"/>八遍。能得除滅五逆重罪及諸業障。燒沈水
<lb n="0401a26" ed="T"/>香欲結界時。或&CB00057;水或&CB00057;灰。或&CB00057;芥子或&CB00057;
<lb n="0401a27" ed="T"/>紫檀木四枚。各七遍釘於四方。一切<note n="0401014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瘧＋（病）【三】</note><note n="0401014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瘧＋（病）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401014"><lem wit="【大】">瘧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">瘧病</rdg></app>寒熱
<lb n="0401a28" ed="T"/>病。作&CB00057;索誦二十一遍繫其<note n="0401015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咽＝胭【三】＊</note><note n="0401015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">咽＝胭【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401015"><lem wit="【大】">咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">胭</rdg></app>下。即得除愈
<lb n="0401a29" ed="T"/>一切諸病。或&CB00057;<note n="0401016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">酥＝蘇【宋】</note><app n="0401016"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蘇</rdg></app>或&CB00057;油或&CB00057;水。各二十一
<pb n="0401b" id="T20.1093.0401b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0401b01" ed="T"/>遍&CB00057;已服之。若欲破他所作&CB00057;<note n="0401017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">咀＝詛【元】【明】</note><app n="0401017"><lem wit="【大】">咀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">詛</rdg></app>。作其人形
<lb n="0401b02" ed="T"/>像。或麵或<note n="0401018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00410;＝泥【三】</note><note n="0401018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00410;＝泥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401018"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00410;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泥</rdg></app>或<note n="0401019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蠟＝臘【三】</note><note n="0401019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠟＝臘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401019"><lem wit="【大】">蠟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">臘</rdg></app>。當以<note n="0401020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鑌＝賓【宋】</note><app n="0401020"><lem wit="【大】">鑌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">賓</rdg></app>鐵為刀段段割
<lb n="0401b03" ed="T"/>之。若有人驚怖欲護身者。當作&CB00057;索帶於身
<lb n="0401b04" ed="T"/>上。若有人患腹痛。&CB00057;鹹水服之。若有人被蟲
<lb n="0401b05" ed="T"/>毒或被蛇螫。當用<note n="0401021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塗＝泥【三】＊</note><note n="0401021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塗＝泥【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401021"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泥</rdg></app>&CB00057;塗之。若有人患眼
<lb n="0401b06" ed="T"/>痛。取白<note n="0401022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綖＝線【三】＊</note><note n="0401022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綖＝線【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401022"><lem wit="【大】">綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>為&CB00057;索繫其耳上。若人患齒。取
<lb n="0401b07" ed="T"/>迦羅毘羅木<note n="0401023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00057;＋（之）【三】</note><note n="0401023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00057;＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401023"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00057;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00057;之</rdg></app>二十一遍。然後嚼之揩磨其
<lb n="0401b08" ed="T"/>齒。欲作大界。取五色<app source="0401022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>&CB00057;二十一遍。取紫
<lb n="0401b09" ed="T"/>檀木四枚為&CB02000;繫索於&CB02000;上纏之。釘著四角
<lb n="0401b10" ed="T"/>即成大界。一者怖處一切驚處欲護身者。當
<lb n="0401b11" ed="T"/>作&CB00057;索帶行。或&CB00057;水灑之或&CB00057;灰用散其上。
<lb n="0401b12" ed="T"/>若有鬼著取五色<app source="0401022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>為&CB00057;索帶之或繫身體。
<lb n="0401b13" ed="T"/>一切寒熱病者。取白<app source="0401022" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">綖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">線</rdg></app>&CB00057;二十一遍作索帶
<lb n="0401b14" ed="T"/>行。若有得一切種種惡瘡。取<note n="0401024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蓽茇＝畢&CB03247;【宋】</note><app n="0401024"><lem wit="【大】">蓽茇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">畢&CB03247;</rdg></app>擣以為末
<lb n="0401b15" ed="T"/>和蜜。&CB00057;二十一遍<note n="0401025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">泥＝塗【三】＊</note><note n="0401025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">泥＝塗【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401025"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">塗</rdg></app>其瘡上。若有人患眼。取
<lb n="0401b16" ed="T"/>香湯或甘草湯。&CB00057;二十一遍洗兩眼。若有人
<lb n="0401b17" ed="T"/>患耳。煮油&CB00057;二十一遍內著耳中。一切&CB00508;諍
<lb n="0401b18" ed="T"/>一切官府一切恐怖處。取水&CB00057;二十一遍洗
<lb n="0401b19" ed="T"/>其面。若國內有大疫病。或城邑聚落。乃至家
<lb n="0401b20" ed="T"/>內當作道場。牛糞<app source="0401021" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">泥</rdg></app>地香湯灑地。於四角處
<lb n="0401b21" ed="T"/>安置新淨水瓶。以種種華置其瓶堙C復將種
<lb n="0401b22" ed="T"/>種華散道場處。持種種飲食皆令香美。復以
<lb n="0401b23" ed="T"/>種種淨草敷設道場。以食置上并諸果蓏。於
<lb n="0401b24" ed="T"/>四角處麵作燈盞。淨布作炷燒諸妙香。以最
<lb n="0401b25" ed="T"/>勝<note n="0401026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上者＝最大【三】</note><note n="0401026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上者＝最大【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401026"><lem wit="【大】">上者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">最大</rdg></app>而作供養。<note n="0401027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其&CB00057;師〕－【三】</note><note n="0401027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其&CB00057;師〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401027"><lem wit="【大】">其&CB00057;師</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>以香湯澡浴著
<lb n="0401b26" ed="T"/>鮮淨衣。於其座上敷新淨褥而坐其上。誦持
<lb n="0401b27" ed="T"/>此&CB00057;一切災變即得消滅。若有遇重病者。將
<lb n="0401b28" ed="T"/>彼瓶水&CB00057;已灑於彼人。凡所灑者即得除滅
<lb n="0401b29" ed="T"/>一切疫病。諸鬼<note n="0401028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">崇＝祟【三】</note><note n="0401028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">崇＝祟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401028"><lem wit="【大】">崇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">祟</rdg></app>者一切有怖畏處。以水灑
<pb n="0401c" id="T20.1093.0401c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0401c01" ed="T"/>之皆得除愈。若有人被他禁&CB00057;。磨栴檀&CB00057;二
<lb n="0401c02" ed="T"/>十一遍。<app source="0401025" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">泥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">塗</rdg></app>其心上即得除愈。若欲除滅一切
<lb n="0401c03" ed="T"/>業障及五逆四重。常誦莫住。若有家內遇<note n="0401029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">疫＝惡疾【三】</note><note n="0401029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">疫＝惡疾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401029"><lem wit="【大】">疫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡疾</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c04" ed="T"/>病。或復諸鬼<note n="0401030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">擾＝繞【宋】，撓【元】【明】</note><note n="0401030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擾＝繞【宋】，＝撓【元】【明】</note><app n="0401030"><lem wit="【大】">擾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">繞</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">撓</rdg></app>亂其家。當取一百八枚蓮華。
<lb n="0401c05" ed="T"/>一一蓮華各&CB00057;一遍。擲著火中即得除愈。若
<lb n="0401c06" ed="T"/>欲取一切眾生心意。當取栴檀一百八枚長
<lb n="0401c07" ed="T"/>二寸。一枚一遍&CB00057;之擲著火中。欲治一切鬼
<lb n="0401c08" ed="T"/>病恐怖之處。當取闍耶草<note n="0401031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔藉草根〕－【三】</note><note n="0401031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔藉草根〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401031"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藉草根</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>毘闍耶草<note n="0401032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔藥〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0401032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔藥〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0401032"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c09" ed="T"/>那句利<app source="0401032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>揵陀那句<note n="0401033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梨＝利【三】</note><note n="0401033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梨＝利【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401033"><lem wit="【大】">梨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">利</rdg></app>草<app source="0401032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><app source="0400010" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">這</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">適</rdg></app>憐尼草<app source="0401032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0401c10" ed="T"/>阿婆耶波&CB00135;草<app source="0401032" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">藥</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>因陀羅波尼草<note n="0401034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">香附子三字三本俱作本文</note><note n="0401034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（香附子）三字夾註＝（香附子）三字本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401034"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">香附子</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">香附子</rdg></app>多迦
<lb n="0401c11" ed="T"/>羅<note n="0401035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">香字三本俱作本文下同</note><note n="0401035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（香）夾註＝（香）本文【宋】下同【元】下同【明】下同</note><app n="0401035"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">香</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">香</rdg></app>斫迦羅<note place="inline">香</note>摩<note n="0401036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＝呵【三】</note><note n="0401036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶＝呵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401036"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">呵</rdg></app>斫迦羅<note place="inline">香</note>毘疏&CB03905;揵多<note place="inline">香</note>
<lb n="0401c12" ed="T"/>蘇摩<note n="0401037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅＝囉【三】</note><note n="0401037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅＝囉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401037"><lem wit="【大】">羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">囉</rdg></app><note n="0401038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是梔子〕－【三】</note><note n="0401038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是梔子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401038"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">是梔子</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0401039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（多草）＋蘇【三】</note><note n="0401039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（多草）＋蘇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401039"><lem wit="【大】">蘇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">多草蘇</rdg></app>難陀<note n="0401040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">草字三本俱作本文</note><note n="0401040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（草）夾註＝（草）本文【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401040"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">草</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">草</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0401c13" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0401c1301">如是諸草。皆搗之作末細羅之。取水和為丸
<lb n="0401c14" ed="T"/>如大棗。&CB00057;一百八遍。或頭戴或繫手而行。一
<lb n="0401c15" ed="T"/>切鬼病一切疫病不能為害。若有小兒著鬼
<lb n="0401c16" ed="T"/>病及疫病所驚怖處。將一丸繫於<app source="0401015" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">咽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">胭</rdg></app>下。若有
<lb n="0401c17" ed="T"/>女人薄相難嫁娶者或有諸病。取此丸藥和
<lb n="0401c18" ed="T"/>水澡浴。即除惡相<note n="0401041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">最妙最勝＝最勝最妙【三】</note><note n="0401041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">最妙最勝＝最勝最妙【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401041"><lem wit="【大】">最妙最勝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">最勝最妙</rdg></app>隨意無難。若有
<lb n="0401c19" ed="T"/>女人不生男者。持藥一丸繫其項即得產男。
<lb n="0401c20" ed="T"/>一切驚怖中皆作大護。若有人被蟲者。此藥
<lb n="0401c21" ed="T"/>亦能破之。帶藥行者不被火燒諸難。若被惡
<lb n="0401c22" ed="T"/>瘡。持此藥塗者<note n="0401042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝則【三】</note><note n="0401042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即＝則【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401042"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">則</rdg></app>得除<note n="0401043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">差＝瘥【三】</note><note n="0401043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差＝瘥【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401043"><lem wit="【大】">差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">瘥</rdg></app>。若有人為諸惡
<lb n="0401c23" ed="T"/>事逼切。帶此藥者即蒙除難。若有人欲除惡
<lb n="0401c24" ed="T"/>風惡雨。&CB00057;水二十一遍散於四方。即得除止。
<lb n="0401c25" ed="T"/>若遇大雹。取一樹枝行&CB00057;遙打之。此觀世音
<lb n="0401c26" ed="T"/>心&CB00057;雖不受持。但誦能破一切業障。能成一
<lb n="0401c27" ed="T"/>切事皆得成就。若有人持此&CB00057;者。彼人當織
<lb n="0401c28" ed="T"/><note n="0401044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一＋（端）【三】</note><note n="0401044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＋（端）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401044"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">一端</rdg></app>白&CB00626;。闊五尺長一丈不得割斷。綜縷彼&CB00626;
<lb n="0401c29" ed="T"/>當畫作一佛。<note n="0401045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綵＝像采【三】</note><note n="0401045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綵＝像采【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401045"><lem wit="【大】">綵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">像采</rdg></app>色中不得用膠。當和香<note n="0401046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">及乳和綵色＝水及以乳汁而用【三】</note><note n="0401046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及乳和綵色＝水及以乳汁而用【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0401046"><lem wit="【大】">及
<pb n="0402a" id="T20.1093.0402a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0402a01" ed="T"/>乳和綵色</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">水及以乳汁而用</rdg></app>畫之。右邊畫作觀世音像。狀如摩
<lb n="0402a02" ed="T"/>醯首羅天。頭上<note n="0402001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">髮＋（毛）【三】</note><note n="0402001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髮＋（毛）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402001"><lem wit="【大】">髮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">髮毛</rdg></app>悉如<note n="0402002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00657;＝螺【三】</note><note n="0402002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00657;＝螺【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402002"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00657;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">螺</rdg></app>髻。方作華冠。肩
<lb n="0402a03" ed="T"/>上當畫作黑鹿皮覆左肩上。自餘身分當畫
<lb n="0402a04" ed="T"/>作種種瓔珞。其畫者教持八關齋勿得雜食。
<lb n="0402a05" ed="T"/>日別香湯清淨澡浴著淨衣裳。其持&CB00057;者當
<lb n="0402a06" ed="T"/>清淨處安像。像前以牛糞塗地。四方齊整縱
<lb n="0402a07" ed="T"/>廣丈六尺。其壇場奡盔瞼桮堙C置八水瓶各
<lb n="0402a08" ed="T"/>受一斗。皆令新淨盛以香湯。復以種種華置
<lb n="0402a09" ed="T"/>其瓶內。安其淨草立八草<note n="0402003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">座＋（座）【三】</note><note n="0402003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">座＋（座）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402003"><lem wit="【大】">座</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">座座</rdg></app>處。安置八方作
<lb n="0402a10" ed="T"/>八分食置其草座上。然後更以六十四分食。
<lb n="0402a11" ed="T"/>各各種種雜美好者。自餘雜食具皆廣大<note n="0402004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔羅列〕－【三】</note><note n="0402004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔羅列〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402004"><lem wit="【大】">羅
<lb n="0402a12" ed="T"/>列</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>作之。<note n="0402005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唯＝惟【三】</note><note n="0402005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402005"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惟</rdg></app>除五辛酒肉。餘但使可得之者皆
<lb n="0402a13" ed="T"/>悉具之。若欲&CB00057;者。當三日三夜斷食燒沈水
<lb n="0402a14" ed="T"/>香。其持&CB00057;<note n="0402006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">人＝者【三】</note><note n="0402006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人＝者【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402006"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">者</rdg></app>以妙香湯三時澡<note n="0402007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">洗＝洒【三】</note><note n="0402007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洗＝洒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402007"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">洒</rdg></app>。大小便
<lb n="0402a15" ed="T"/>時皆須澡浴。若不能三日三夜者。但一日一
<lb n="0402a16" ed="T"/>夜斷食。當食三種白食乳酪粳米。在彼像前
<lb n="0402a17" ed="T"/>長跪設飲食已。當誦&CB00057;一千八遍。爾時<note n="0402008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔行者〕－【三】</note><note n="0402008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔行者〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402008"><lem wit="【大】">行者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0402a18" ed="T"/>在於像前。即見自身出大光明猶如火焰。既
<lb n="0402a19" ed="T"/>自見已生大歡欣。乃至觀世音菩薩自來現
<lb n="0402a20" ed="T"/>身。隨其心願皆悉與之。若欲隱身。當取雌黃
<lb n="0402a21" ed="T"/>或石黛。擣令碎末精細羅之。在於像前&CB00057;一
<lb n="0402a22" ed="T"/>千八遍。塗於眼上即得隱身。乃至騰空飛行。
<lb n="0402a23" ed="T"/>復得三昧名不空智<note n="0402009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝現【三】</note><note n="0402009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">見＝現【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0402009"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">現</rdg></app>在莊嚴。作如是法已。
<lb n="0402a24" ed="T"/>然後凡所作者皆得成就。此是持&CB00057;法我今
<lb n="0402a25" ed="T"/>說竟。</p>
<lb n="0402a26" ed="T"/><p id="pT20p0402a2601">爾時佛說此經已。時觀世音菩薩摩訶薩。及
<lb n="0402a27" ed="T"/>淨居諸天子娑婆世界主大梵天王。及諸菩
<lb n="0402a28" ed="T"/>薩眾諸聲聞眾一切大眾人民。聞觀世音菩
<lb n="0402a29" ed="T"/>薩對佛說此經。皆大歡喜奉行。</p>
<pb n="0402b" id="T20.1093.0402b" ed="T"/>
